ua.training.model.knight

Class Knight

  • java.lang.Object
    • ua.training.model.knight.Knight
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAmmunitionCarrier

    public class Knight
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAmmunitionCarrier
    Implementation of IAmmunitionCarrier interface, which presents knight. Class contains collection of ammunition and methods to work with it. To create instance of this class use KnightBuilder.
    See Also:
    IAmmunitionCarrier, KnightBuilder
